modName: Viking King Ragnar Lodbrok RaceMenu Preset
summary: Play as the only true King
descriptionHtml:
[size=3][u]Required Mods[/u]: (Download and install them in this order)

SKSE: http://skse.silverlock.org/
SkyUI: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863/?
RaceMenu Mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624//?
ShowRaceMenu Precache Killer: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33526/?
The Eyes Of Beauty: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
Companion Valfar: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25360/?


[color=#efefef][u]Recommended Mods[/u]:

The Veteran Skin : http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81004/?[b][i][u][s]
[/s][/u][/i][/b][/color]

[u]HOW TO INSTALL[/u] [i]: 

[/i]1. Download and install with NMM/MO, or manually install by extracting it into your Data folder.[i]

[/i]
[u]HOW TO USE[/u]:

1. Go in-game and type SHOWRACEMENU into console.
2. Select race Bretone
3. Go to the PRESETS Tab and hit F9 and load the preset.
4. You're done![i][s]
[/s][/i][/size]
